sentence: how many rivers are in the state that has the most rivers ?
sentence-with-vars: how many rivers are in the state that has the most rivers ?
sql: select max ( tmp.rivers ) from ( select count ( river.river_name ) as rivers , traverse from river group by traverse ) as tmp ;
